caption: The hotel is awesome... It's a little away from main market but that's what makes this place more beautiful. The place is neat and clean and beautifully maintained. The food was delicious and they had a lot many options. Over all its too good.

TGL is Awesome!! Stunning Views, Superb Hospitality, Delicious Food!! Sorry for the long review, but there is so much to write about the resort. Our experience just kept getting better. We were searching for a good resort in Mahabaleshwar for our 1st Wedding Anniversary celebration and our search ended with The Grand Legacy. Booking experience -- We contacted the resort directly and Swapnil helped us with different room options. Very knowledgeable guy who explained about different room options nicely, so we could make an informed decision. Arrival -- This resort is very close from the main Panchgani ‚Äì Mahabaleshwar main road. We did not have any problems locating the resort. Our Welcome was warm. Check-in was hassle free and seamless. View and Ambience -- THE BEST PART. The location of the resort is such that it is surrounded by a picturesque view of the mountain range and green landscape. It doesn‚Äôt matter which room you choose; you are in for the best view. Even a stroll inside the resort was amazing. Night view of the property, the restaurant and the pool is breathtaking!! Rooms & Housekeeping ‚Äì We opted for the Aqua and Maharaja Suite. The Aqua suite is huge, with a private pool and jacuzzi. As the name suggests, stay in Maharaja suite is ‚ÄúLiving like a Maharaja‚Äù. The unique wooden interiors, artefacts, curtains, nightlamps, the cushions gave us a Royal feel. Housekeeping was at our service at the very next minute. (Don‚Äôt miss the room pics I uploaded) Food ‚Äì Food in TGL is at the next level. The taste and food quality cannot be explained in words. One needs to enjoy the delicious treat in person. On our special request, the management made a Candlelight dinner arrangement besides the pool with lip-smacking food and a cake. The interior of the restaurant is very classy with unique chandelier and lamps. The food here is pure vegetarian, however if you are a non-vegetarian, you will not regret your dining experience at TGL. The entire staff of The Grand Legacy resort is courteous, prompt and so humble. Overall experience was 10/10. We are looking forward to recreate beautiful memories soon üòä
